- **Role:** {job_title}
- **Manager:** {manager_name}
- **Start Date:** {start_date}
- **Salary:** ${salary} (per year/hour)
- **Bonus (if any):** {bonus_details}
- **Equity (if any):** {equity_details}
- **Company:** {company_name}
- **Deadline to Accept:** {deadline_date}

### Output Format
**Subject: Job Offer from {company_name}**

Dear {candidate_name},

Following our recent conversations, we are delighted to offer you the position of {job_title} at {company_name}, starting on {start_date}.

You will report to {manager_name}. Your starting salary will be ${salary} per {year/hour}, paid {pay_frequency}.

[**Optional Bonus/Equity:** In addition, you will be eligible for {bonus_details} and {equity_details}.]

This offer is contingent upon {contingencies} (e.g., 'a successful background check', 'signing the attached {document_name}').

Please find the full details of your offer, including our benefits package, attached.

To accept this offer, please sign and return this letter by {deadline_date}.

We are incredibly excited to have you join our team. 

Sincerely,
{my_name}
{my_title}
{company_name}

